research_municipality_step.notes: Missouri City, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government, which is categorized as 'mayor_council' for this response. Mayor Robin J. Elackatt was re-elected for a third term in an election with early voting totals reported on November 4, 2025. Sonya Brown-Marshall, Lynn Clouser, and Sharita Thompson were also confirmed as leading in their respective council positions in the November 2025 election. For council members Monica Riley, Johanna Ouderkirk, and Floyd Emery, specific divisions were not detailed in the search results, so they are listed without divisions, implying at-large positions if not specified otherwise by the city.
